The paper discusses using web page titles to rediscover lost web pages, which suggests a focus on information retrieval (cs.IR) and web search (cs.DL). The paper also mentions conducting tests based on elements of the title, which could fall under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper's focus on web pages and their status (found or not found) could also relate to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
